<font color="#FF0000">Akha gûm-ishi ashi gurum</font>
<font color="#FFFF00">(Here in the void, only death)</font>

246
03:03:12,233 --> 03:03:23,900
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ I tuo i macil a staldaron</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(The strength, the weapon, the needs of the valiant)</font></i>

247
03:03:24,233 --> 03:03:32,200
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ Marinyë Cor[ma]</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Let the Ring be your weapon)</font></i>

248
03:03:32,233 --> 03:03:45,200
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ I tuo i macil a lelyat túrenna</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(The strength, the weapon, go to victory!)</font></i>

249
03:06:40,000 --> 03:06:55,000
<i><font color="#FF0000">♫ Ash Burz-Durbagu burzum-ishi</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(One for the Dark Lord on his dark throne)</font></i>

250
03:07:58,970 --> 03:08:16,459
<i><font color="#008000">♫ Ú-velin i vegil an aegas</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(I do not love the bright sword for its sharpness)</font></i>

251
03:08:16,970 --> 03:08:38,459
<i><font color="#008000">♫ Egor i... bilin a linn[as]</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Nor the... arrow for its swiftness)</font></i>

252
03:08:48,233 --> 03:09:00,200
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ I alda helda, i ehtelë lína</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(The tree is bare, the fountain still)</font></i>

253
03:09:01,233 --> 03:09:16,200
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ Manna lelyalye Voromírë?</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Whither goest thou Boromir?)</font></i>

254
03:09:18,233 --> 03:09:35,200
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ Cánalya desse sí mas[së]</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(We heard your call but cannot find you)</font></i>

255
03:13:28,970 --> 03:13:50,459
<i><font color="#008000">♫ Ú-velin i ve[gil]</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(I do not love the bright sword)</font></i>

256
03:21:14,808 --> 03:21:20,365
<i>♫ Shines down upon you</i>

257
03:21:21,968 --> 03:21:28,032
<i>♫ May it be when darkness falls</i>

258
03:21:28,056 --> 03:21:34,625
<i>♫ Your heart will be true</i>

259
03:21:35,212 --> 03:21:41,387
<i>♫ You walk a lonely road</i>

260
03:21:41,411 --> 03:21:50,922
<i>♫ Oh! How far you are from home</i>

261
03:21:52,002 --> 03:22:03,585
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ Mornie utúlië</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Darkness has come)</font></i>

262
03:22:03,609 --> 03:22:15,526
<i>♫ Believe and you will find your way</i>

263
03:22:15,550 --> 03:22:27,968
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ Mornie alantië</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Darkness has fallen)</font></i>

264
03:22:27,992 --> 03:22:39,402
<i>♫ A promise lives within you now</i>

265
03:22:42,558 --> 03:22:48,609
<i>♫ May it be the shadow's call</i>

266
03:22:48,633 --> 03:22:54,086
<i>♫ Will fly away</i>

267
03:22:55,632 --> 03:23:01,537
<i>♫ May it be you journey on</i>

268
03:23:01,561 --> 03:23:06,927
<i>♫ To light the day</i>

269
03:23:08,066 --> 03:23:14,415
<i>♫ When the night is overcome</i>

270
03:23:14,439 --> 03:23:23,212
<i>♫ You may rise to find the sun</i>

271
03:23:23,402 --> 03:23:36,000
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ Mornie utúlië</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Darkness has come)</font></i>

272
03:23:36,173 --> 03:23:47,753
<i>♫ Believe and you will find your way</i>

273
03:23:47,778 --> 03:23:59,532
<i><font color="#0080C0">♫ Mornie alantië</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Darkness has fallen)</font></i>

274
03:23:59,556 --> 03:24:11,965
<i>♫ A promise lives within you now</i>

275
03:24:11,991 --> 03:24:24,076
<i>♫ A promise lives within you...</i>

276
03:24:24,100 --> 03:24:31,400
<i>♫ ...now</i>

277
03:25:08,430 --> 03:25:14,835
<i>♫ When the cold of winter comes</i>

278
03:25:14,859 --> 03:25:21,206
<i>♫ Starless night will cover day</i>

279
03:25:21,230 --> 03:25:27,396
<i>♫ In the veiling of the sun</i>

280
03:25:27,420 --> 03:25:34,353
<i>♫ We will walk in bitter rain</i>

281
03:25:34,640 --> 03:25:39,676
<i>♫ But in dreams</i>

282
03:25:39,700 --> 03:25:46,670
<i>♫ I can hear your name</i>

283
03:25:46,694 --> 03:25:52,592
<i>♫ And in dreams</i>

284
03:25:52,616 --> 03:26:03,703
<i>♫ We will meet again</i>

285
03:26:22,376 --> 03:26:28,229
<i>♫ When the seas and mountains fall</i>

286
03:26:28,254 --> 03:26:34,946
<i>♫ And we come, to end of days</i>

287
03:26:34,970 --> 03:26:41,244
<i>♫ In the dark I hear a call</i>

288
03:26:41,268 --> 03:26:44,344
<i>♫ Calling me there</i>

289
03:26:44,765 --> 03:26:47,931
<i>♫ I will go there</i>

290
03:26:47,955 --> 03:26:53,115
<i>♫ And back again.</i>

291
03:26:53,139 --> 03:27:13,339
<i><font color="#008000">♫ A, Elbereth Gilthoniel</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(O, Elbereth Kindler of Stars)</font></i>

292
03:27:13,363 --> 03:27:35,025
<i><font color="#008000">♫ silivren penna míriel</font></i>
<i><font color="#FFFF00">(Glittering light falling like shining jewels)</font></i>
